## 4. Complete Data Flow Timing Analysis

### 4.1 Stream 1: Patient Data (Real-Time)
```
EHR Event → Harmonizer:         50-100ms
Harmonizer → Kafka:              10-20ms
Kafka → Flink:                   5-10ms
Flink Processing:                100-500ms (depends on complexity)
Flink → Insight Topic:           10-20ms
Insight → FHIR Store:            50-100ms
Insight → Push Notification:     20-50ms
-------------------------------------------
Total E2E Latency:               245-800ms
```

### 4.2 Stream 2: Knowledge Updates (Near-Real-Time)
```
KB Update → PostgreSQL WAL:      1-5ms
WAL → Debezium:                  100-500ms
Debezium → Kafka:                10-20ms
Kafka → Adapter:                 5-10ms
Adapter Processing:              1-3 seconds
Adapter → Neo4j:                 100-500ms
Adapter → Redis:                 10-50ms
-------------------------------------------
Total Sync Latency:              1.2-4.1 seconds
```

